## Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run in development mode
npm run start:dev

# Run tests
npm test

# Build
npm run build
```

## Deployment

```bash
# Deploy to local environment
forge deploy --env=local

# Deploy to dev
forge deploy --env=dev

# Deploy to production
forge deploy --env=prod
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /` - Hello endpoint
- `GET /health` - Health check

## Configuration

Service configuration is managed in `forge.json` at the workspace root.
Environment-specific Helm values are in `deploy/helm/values-{env}.yaml`.
